WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.441
欢迎来到最后一个教程！让我们确保你的磁盘再也不会耗尽。我们将在线扩展一个已满的

00:00:05.441 --> 00:00:09.882
repository，把删除释放的空间还给

00:00:09.882 --> 00:00:14.322
pool，然后让机器自动完成这两件事。

00:00:15.082 --> 00:00:17.858
来看看这个模型。每个 repository

00:00:17.858 --> 00:00:20.633
都是共享 datastore

00:00:20.633 --> 00:00:23.409
pool 中的一个文件。repository

00:00:23.409 --> 00:00:26.184
可以在线扩展，同时 container

00:00:26.184 --> 00:00:28.960
继续运行。但在 repo

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:31.735
内部删除数据本身并不会释放任何空间。Trim 才是把数据块还给

00:00:31.735 --> 00:00:34.511
pool 的操作。而

00:00:34.511 --> 00:00:37.286
policy 则将两者都自动化了。

00:00:40.557 --> 00:00:43.182
Fill the repository most of the way

00:00:43.182 --> 00:00:43.932
and check:

00:00:43.932 --> 00:00:45.808
the filesystem is getting tight.

00:00:51.331 --> 00:00:53.369
快满了。是时候扩容了。

00:00:56.650 --> 00:00:57.939
Grow it online.

00:00:57.939 --> 00:01:00.517
The encrypted container and the filesystem

00:01:00.517 --> 00:01:03.096
expand while the containers keep running

00:01:03.096 --> 00:01:04.385
— zero downtime,

00:01:04.385 --> 00:01:05.244
zero unmount.

00:01:08.244 --> 00:01:11.327
现在是四 GB。没有任何重启。

00:01:14.617 --> 00:01:15.978
Verify from inside:

00:01:15.978 --> 00:01:16.886
same volume,

00:01:16.886 --> 00:01:18.248
double the room.

00:01:22.546 --> 00:01:24.584
应用程序毫无察觉。

00:01:27.877 --> 00:01:29.293
Now the other direction.

00:01:29.293 --> 00:01:31.772
Delete the big file — but watch:

00:01:31.772 --> 00:01:34.605
the pool does not get the space back

00:01:34.605 --> 00:01:34.959
yet.

00:01:34.959 --> 00:01:37.437
Deleted blocks stay reserved inside the image.

00:01:39.187 --> 00:01:42.819
在 repo 内部已释放，但仍归镜像所有。

00:01:46.139 --> 00:01:48.794
Trim hands those blocks back to the datastore

00:01:48.794 --> 00:01:49.126
pool,

00:01:49.126 --> 00:01:49.458
online.

00:01:49.458 --> 00:01:51.781
This is the step most setups forget.

00:01:55.024 --> 00:01:58.263
已回收。存储池再次畅通。

00:02:01.539 --> 00:02:03.952
Now stop doing this by hand.

00:02:03.952 --> 00:02:06.768
The policy enables automatic growth up to

00:02:06.768 --> 00:02:08.378
a ceiling you choose,

00:02:08.378 --> 00:02:09.584
plus scheduled trims.

00:02:15.355 --> 00:02:17.706
策略已保存。接下来由机器接管。

00:02:20.984 --> 00:02:22.135
Read it back:

00:02:22.135 --> 00:02:22.903
auto-grow on,

00:02:22.903 --> 00:02:24.438
ceiling at eight gigabytes,

00:02:24.438 --> 00:02:25.973
trim on a schedule.

00:02:30.121 --> 00:02:32.237
设置一次，从此无需操心。

00:02:35.530 --> 00:02:38.439
And the view that ties it together:

00:02:38.439 --> 00:02:40.934
storage health shows every repo's usage,

00:02:40.934 --> 00:02:41.765
the pool,

00:02:41.765 --> 00:02:44.675
and how much copy-on-write sharing is saving

00:02:44.675 --> 00:02:45.090
you.

00:02:45.090 --> 00:02:48.800
一个视图：使用情况、节省量和扩展空间。

00:02:49.578 --> 00:02:59.452
系列到此结束！十八个教程，从安装到存储自动驾驶。你的服务器又回到你手中了。感谢收看！
